data.description: LOCATION LOCATION! This gorgeous 3/2.5/2 is in the shadows of downtown, a couple a minutes away from the Med Center and walking distance to the museum district. In great move in condition with recent paint and brand-new carpet. Downstairs you have a living and dining area separated by a 2-sided fireplace. Also down is the kitchen with recent appliances, granite counters and 42 " cabinets. Upstairs you have 3 bedrooms that includes a large master suite. This big master has 2 separate closets, huge jacuzzi bath with separate shower and dual sinks. The was roof is less then 2 yrs. old.
